scopes.name: schedule_only
scopes.explanation: Lines 9-321 comprise the full Schedule to the ISDA Master Agreement, starting with the heading 'SCHEDULE' and including all the 'Parts' (1-5) and their provisions. The content after line 321 (Annexure 1, Definitions Schedule, and the Credit Support Annex) is outside the main Schedule. The lines before line 9 are cover, parties, and standard preamble, not part of the Schedule.
